hment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="gfriend j-hope bts day6 kpop concerts tours asia 2025" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/gfriend-j-hope-bts-day-8-k-pop-concerts-tours-asia-2025.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/gfriend-j-hope-bts-day-8-k-pop-concerts-tours-asia-2025-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/gfriend-j-hope-bts-day-8-k-pop-concerts-tours-asia-2025-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/gfriend-j-hope-bts-day-8-k-pop-concerts-tours-asia-2025-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/gfriend-j-hope-bts-day-8-k-pop-concerts-tours-asia-2025-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/gfriend-j-hope-bts-day-8-k-pop-concerts-tours-asia-2025-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Borders are open, live music is back and the <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/k-pop">K-pop</a> touring cycle is in full swing. Stars including veteran idols <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gfriend">GFRIEND</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/day6">Day6</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/j-hope">J-hope</a> and more are touring the world with both new and old tunes in tow – and hitting Asia very soon.</p><p> While some of those artists are staging their own headline shows, others are on the line-ups of music festivals with both multi-genre and Hallyu-only line-ups. The announcements have been coming thick and fast of late so <em>NME</em> &#39;s decided to help with a handy list of K-pop concerts and music festivals in Asia for 2025.</p><p> Scroll down to see if your favourite <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/k-pop">K-pop</a> artist is touring Asia and get info on cities, dates, venues, tickets and more.</p><h2> J-hope </h2><figure id="attachment_3827736" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827736" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"